+#[mutable]
+enum Foo { A }
+
+fn bar<T: Const>(_: T) {}
+
+fn main() {
+    let x = A;
+    bar(x); //~ ERROR instantiating a type parameter with an incompatible type `Foo`, which does not fulfill `Const`
+}
